Key Match Events: David Brooks scored the opening goal for Wales in the 3rd minute
Neco Williams scored the second goal for Wales in the 38th minute
Teemu Pukki scored Finland's only goal in the 45th minute
Brennan Johnson scored the third goal for Wales in the 47th minute
Dan James scored the fourth goal for Wales in the 87th minute
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played in Cardiff, Wales
The winner of the play-off final will qualify for Euro 2024
Others: The match was broadcast on S4C and BBC Radio 5 live
Rob Page is the manager of the Wales national team
